  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1126">
<l>kaṇṇuḷḷiṟ pōkā rimaippiṟ paruvarār</l>
<l> nuṇṇiyareṅ kāta lavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My lover would not depart from mine eyes; even if I wink, he would not suffer (from pain); he is so ethereal.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
